    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem); font-weight:400; font-variation-settings:'opsz' 32; line-height:1.2; color:#191817; margin-bottom:2.5rem;">Common questions about Bald Hills.</h2>
    <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column;">

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#191817; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What drives property values in Bald Hills?
          <span style="color:#b98229; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Block size, position relative to the Pine River and proximity to Bald Hills train station are the primary value drivers in Bald Hills. Larger family-sized allotments on the elevated southern side of the suburb, well clear of the river overlay, consistently attract stronger interest than smaller post-war blocks closer to the river. Properties within walking distance of the train station carry a clear premium with commuter families.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#191817; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          How long does it take to sell a home in Bald Hills?
          <span style="color:#b98229; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Well-priced Bald Hills homes typically sell within 25 to 50 days. The suburb attracts a mixed buyer pool including first home buyers using the southern Moreton Bay value gap, families targeting St Paul's School and the train station, and investors who follow Bracken Ridge and Strathpine yield patterns. Campaign length depends largely on which of these segments your property is best positioned for.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#191817; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What is the lifestyle like in Bald Hills?
          <span style="color:#b98229; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Bald Hills offers a quiet outer-northern lifestyle anchored by the Pine River parklands, the Bald Hills train station and easy access to Westfield Strathpine and the Carseldine retail precinct. The suburb suits families and first home buyers who want larger blocks and genuine green space within a rail-line commute of the CBD, without paying inner or middle ring prices.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#191817; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          Is Bald Hills a good suburb to buy in right now?
          <span style="color:#b98229; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Bald Hills sits on the southern edge of the Moreton Bay growth corridor and benefits from both the City of Brisbane address and the train line that puts the CBD within reach. Families priced out of Bridgeman Downs and Aspley regularly find better block sizes here at meaningfully lower prices. The combination of St Paul's School, the train station and the river parkland creates underlying demand that has supported steady value growth even when the broader outer-northern market has softened.</p>
      </details>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

